channel.title: Moving Object
channel.description:
Trying to delete practice dummies from king lathas' training grounds but inside the ObjectManager they are not there.
I checked to see if they were just under a different ID but couldnt find one. I also typed in my coords and STILL nothing.

item.title: Moving Object
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Pro tip: the game has more than one object type. Just because you told the game to delete the object at X, Y, Z with type 10, would not remove the object at X, Y, Z with type 0.

Read full topic

item.title: Moving Object
item.dc:creator: @WarTusk-RSPS WarTusk-RSPS
item.description:
@WarTusk-RSPS wrote:

X-J-K-X:

Most of the objects in the world aren’t in your object manager or object spawns, they’re part of the world itself. There are methods to delete objects on specific tiles

Just like what X-J-K-X said and I also sent you some stuff on skype mate to help you out if you are still stuck.
